WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.280
Hello! Today I'll show you how to connect the station to Wi-Fi.

00:04.280 --> 00:11.640
You'll need a mouse — plug it into the USB port on the side of the station.

00:11.640 --> 00:19.280
Right-click, then left-click the square, and close the rental app.

00:19.280 --> 00:25.520
Next, click on Settings and open "Network & Internet".

00:25.960 --> 00:30.160
This part works the same as setting up Wi-Fi on a regular phone or tablet.

00:30.160 --> 00:37.160
Pick the Wi-Fi option, select your network, and enter the password.

00:43.000 --> 00:49.000
Then tap "Connect" and the station will join the network.

00:50.000 --> 01:02.000
Now press the circle button, swipe the screen up, and open the rental app again.

01:02.000 --> 01:08.000
Done! Remove the mouse — the station is now connected to Wi-Fi.
